archimate:BusinessObject.name: Material Test Specification
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation: The Material Test Specification corresponds to the ISA-95 object type MaterialTestSpecificationType: "This is typically used to specify a material test specification to determine a value for a property. An instance of a MaterialTestSpecificationType may test one or more of these items." (https://reference.opcfoundation.org/ISA-95/v100/docs/8.4.3.1 )
